frontmatter.description: Status of excluding the selected faces and features in the cut list sort exclusion list.

title: swCutListExclusionStatus_e
description: Status of excluding the selected faces and features in the cut list sort exclusion list.

values.description: = Selected faces and features are invalid because they are not of selection type BODYFEATURE or FACE. Other examples of face and features that are invalid for exclusion: Chamfers that remove an entire face. Suppressed features. Features that create new bodies from sketches, such as boss-extrude, revolve, and sweep. Certain sheet metal features.
